Q3.Increasing Triangle Pattern
* 
* * 
* * * 
* * * * 
* * * * * 
Approch-1
---------
num=5
for i in range(num):
    print("* "*(i+1))
Approch-2
---------
for i in range(num):
    for j in range(i+1):
        print("*",end=' ')
    print()
Q4.Decreasing Triangle Pattern.
* * * * * * 
* * * * * 
* * * * 
* * * 
* * 
*
Approch-1
---------
num=5
for i in range(num,-1,-1):
    for j in range(i+1):
        print("*",end=' ')
    print()
Approch-2
---------
n=6
for i in range(n):
    for j in range(i,n):
        print("*",end=' ')
    print()
